Text:
@wiredcitroen and anyone else who gas trouble with this.

From the CRACK Folder copy the "WebBuilder" Application file to the installation folder and OVERWRITE the file. Then launch WebBuilder, when the prompt pops up enter the email and serial from the KEY text file in the crack folder.

You should get "Activation Successful" or recognized by the Activation Servers message or something like that and be good to go.

You an also download the app from the website and patch that also.

Cheers ;)
